00:02:52.464 --> 00:02:54.382 position:50% align:center
I think the building's
kinda cute.

00:02:54.466 --> 00:02:56.217 position:50% align:center
I don't think
I quite understand.

00:02:56.301 --> 00:02:58.261 position:50% align:center
