it up on my phone?

00:03:01.097 --> 00:03:02.098 position:50% align:center
[INO, ROKO]
"Temple.

00:03:02.182 --> 00:03:03.933 position:50% align:center
A building or facility
that serves as

00:03:04.017 --> 00:03:06.644 position:50% align:center
