for a particular field."

00:03:06.728 --> 00:03:08.021 position:50% align:center
Oh, I get it now.

00:03:08.104 --> 00:03:09.606 position:50% align:center
[HOHO]
Yes, that's right!

00:03:09.689 --> 00:03:11.358 position:50% align:center
This place has history!

00:03:11.441 --> 00:03:13.693 position:50% align:center
[HAYU] It's been a while since
I've visited the office!

00:03:13.777 --> 00:03:17.113 position:50% align:center
[NINA] Yeah, me too. We don't
get to come out here often.

00:03:17.197 --> 00:03:19.991 position:50% align:center
But the fact that all of us were
called in together isn't good.

00:03:20.075 --> 00:03:22.577 position:50% align:center
I'm worried they really
are going to cancel our show.

00:03:22.660 --> 00:03:24.162 position:50% align:center
