00:03:24.245 --> 00:03:25.997 position:50% align:center
Wait, but if the show gets cut,
does that mean the entire group

00:03:26.081 --> 00:03:27.540 position:50% align:center
will be kicked out
of the Mouse House?

00:03:27.624 --> 00:03:29.125 position:50% align:center
Are we all going to be homeless?

00:03:29.209 --> 00:03:30.752 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:03:30.835 --> 00:03:32.504 position:50% align:center
A homeless idol group.

00:03:32.587 --> 00:03:34.756 position:50% align:center
Could this be
the next big thing?

00:03:34.839 --> 00:03:36.299 position:50% align:center
Bad idea!

00:03:36.383 --> 00:03:39.719 position:50% align:center
Oh, relax. There's no reason to
be so worried about a meeting.

00:03:39.803 --> 00:03:42.055 position:50% align:center
