about that, you'll see.

00:03:42.138 --> 00:03:43.682 position:50% align:center
You sure about that?

00:03:43.765 --> 00:03:45.558 position:50% align:center
[HOHO] Look, a zero
percent average rating

00:03:45.642 --> 00:03:48.311 position:50% align:center
