House Hearthrob" segment!

00:04:03.993 --> 00:04:05.537 position:50% align:center
Uh-oh!

00:04:06.579 --> 00:04:08.415 position:50% align:center
"Uh-oh"?

00:04:08.498 --> 00:04:09.958 position:50% align:center
[OTO giggles]

00:04:10.041 --> 00:04:12.210 position:50% align:center
Well, hello there,
ladies of Fruit Tart!

00:04:12.293 --> 00:04:14.504 position:50% align:center
I was getting tired
of waiting for you!

00:04:14.587 --> 00:04:16.464 position:50% align:center
[BOTH gasps]

00:04:16.548 --> 00:04:19.217 position:50% align:center
What does an elementary-
school student want with us?

00:04:19.300 --> 00:04:20.719 position:50% align:center
Hey, guys, what do you think--

00:04:20.802 --> 00:04:22.012 position:50% align:center
Stop it!

00:04:22.095 --> 00:04:24.806 position:50% align:center
